UR  - https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/030440769390081F
AB  - The iterative algorithm suggested by Greene (1982) for the estimation of stochastic frontier production models does not necessarily solve the likelihood equations. Corrected iterative algorithms which generalize Fair's method (1977) and solve the likelihood equations are derived. These algorithms are compared with the Newton method in an empirical case. The Newton method is more time saving than these algorithms.
